/**
 * This script counts the number of spots of different classes per cells 
 * (spots should be PointsROI objects, ideally generated by spotiflow).
 * 
 * The number of spots of each class is added a measurement to the corresonding cell.
 * 
 * Assumptions
 *     - all spots are assigned to a class (this can be achieve by activating 
 *     'setClassChannelName()' in the qupath extension spotiflow builder.
 *     - Resolve hierarchy should be done prior to run the script. If you are using spotiflow extension,
 *      cellpose, stardist, or instanseg extension, hierarchy is already resolved.
 * 
 * 
 * author: Rémy Dornier - PTBIOP & Claude.ai
 * date: 2025-05.29
 * version: 1.0.0
 * 
 * Last tested on QuPath 0.7.x
